<topic id="d1e56"><title>5.6 Vector Triple Products</title><body><p>
The volume of a parallelepiped with sides 
<d4p_eqn_inline>
  <d4p_MathML><m:math xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline" overflow="scroll"><m:mrow><m:mover accent="true"><m:mi>A</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="true">⟶</m:mo></m:mover><m:mo>,</m:mo><m:mover accent="true"><m:mi>B</m:mi><m:mo stretchy="true">⟶</m:mo></m:mover></m:mrow></m:math></d4p_MathML>
